data.description: Charming 2 bed, 1 bath home in Greeley with endless character! Enter into a bright living room with large windows and original hardwood floors. The open floor plan allows for views of the kitchen and living room with a countertop bar area to separate the space. The original hardwood floors extend down the hall and into the two bedrooms. The bathroom has been updated with beautiful tile, vanity, sink, bathtub and fixtures. The kitchen features tile counters, dishwasher, disposal, microwave, refrigerator and newer stainless steel double oven - all included in the sale! Just off the kitchen is the laundry room/mudroom area. The washer and dryer are also included. Walk out to a large fenced backyard that backs to open land and includes a fire pit, storage shed and covered patio that is ready to be enjoyed year round. New windows (2 years old), New Roof (3 years old) and New Furnace with Ecobee with Alexa system and sensors (3 years old)! Walking distance to parks, bus stop and close to Olde Town Greeley and UNC. Come see this home today!
